{"tid":970613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 澳門計劃調動千億儲備　部份交予廣東省政府投資","createTime":"2019-01-06T03:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T11:26:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"97967533c608ebe5caa3866e91396c5babbffe7b","tid":970613,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"澳門計劃調動千億儲備　部份交予廣東省政府投資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E8%AA%BF%E5%8B%95%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%84%B2%E5%82%99-%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%88%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87/?fbclid=IwAR0HDL4flmQtyao-UVSiEN23_GfmJJV5LumQ1zxKbpiQqsuf9xF4RMEcflk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%2582%2599-%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0HDL4flmQtyao-UVSiEN23_GfmJJV5LumQ1zxKbpiQqsuf9xF4RMEcflk&d=ao9E%2F6OdHCl1a577d6iu3Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e7a8109f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%2582%2599-%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0HDL4flmQtyao-UVSiEN23_GfmJJV5LumQ1zxKbpiQqsuf9xF4RMEcflk&h=858f1831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E8%AA%BF%E5%8B%95%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%84%B2%E5%82%99-%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%88%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87/?fbclid=IwAR0HDL4flmQtyao-UVSiEN23_GfmJJV5LumQ1zxKbpiQqsuf9xF4RMEcflk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">澳門特區去年的儲備逾3千億澳門幣，但回報率卻低見2%。澳門經濟財政司司長梁維特昨披露，會將部分儲備透過廣東省政府與及國家開發銀行投資，以賺取更高回報。<br />\n<br />\n《南方都市報》今日報道，澳門政府目前擁有2078億多元的超額儲備、1343億多元基本儲備，但是去年的投資回報率只有約2%，跑輸通脹。梁維特昨日在立法會表示，計劃將特區儲備的投資款項分別用於廣東省政府和國家開發銀行。</span><br />\n<br />\n計劃中投放至廣東省政府的款項會被用於投資項目，回報率大約在4%-5%，省政府確保會保本保息。至於另一筆款項則透過國家開發銀行保證回報，通過中葡發展基金找一些項目投資，追求合理回報。但他亦承認，要追贏去年約6.05%的通脹率並不容易。<br />\n<br />\n但梁維特節未有透露具體要將多少儲備，投放到何處。他解釋由於法律並未規定儲備的超額上限是多少，故先要確定一個儲備運用的安全線。超出安全線的的部分可成立基金，與社會福利支出掛鉤。另外財政儲備的投資亦需按照一定比例。<br />\n<br />\n另外據《澳門日報》報道，有議員詢問澳門會否以獨立地區身份，參與中國牽頭的「亞投行」以利經濟建設。梁維特指政府正密切留意動態，會支持及配合中央的倡議，並做好準備在適當時間及條件下，思考用哪種形式支持及配合。"},{"pid":"f84927ef0bffb7aec93464b971dd47ee6bb90b6a","tid":970613,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:44:20.000Z","msg":"救國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f6e15f51ef9c6912baf22f35e3c2b1ea1197fc","tid":970613,"uid":21432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"有無公佈過依家賺左幾多？<br />\n係咪借左俾巴基懶坦收唔返？"},{"pid":"ea01a4af7f2c1902825692003bdd5f507f3ee143","tid":970613,"uid":92734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"輸淨幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f62bc0a69ed700997e3dffad2f96b4ac274db9","tid":970613,"uid":26329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea01a4af7f2c1902825692003bdd5f507f3ee143","tid":970613,"uid":92734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"輸淨幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"貪淨幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379cd793cdc5dbba56404ebcfba994610a93965a","tid":970613,"uid":53705,"lik